'''Hammersonic Festival''' is a [[heavy metal music|heavy metal]] [[music festival|festival]] held annually at [[Jakarta]] in Indonesia. It is the biggest [[music festival|festival]] in [[South East Asia]].

Notable bands that have performed in Hammersonic are [[Tarja (band)|Tarja]], [[Bullet For My Valentine]], [[Hatebreed]], [[Morbid Angel]], [[Fleshgod Apocalypse]], [[Belphegor (band)|Belphegor]] [[Cradle Of Filth]], [[Lamb of God (band)|Lamb of God]] , [[As I Lay Dying (band)|As I Lay Dying]], [[Epica (band)|Epica]], [[Cannibal Corpse]], [[Obituary (band)|Obituary]], [[Kreator]], [[Destruction (band)|Destruction]], [[Dying Fetus]], [[Nile (band)|Nile]], [[Lock Up (UK band)|Lock up]], [[Suffocation (band)|Suffocation]], [[Dirty Rotten Imbeciles]], [[Hour of Penance]], [[Chthonic (band)]], [[Angra (band)|Angra]], [[Vader (band)|Vader]], [[Gorgoroth (band)|Gorgoroth]], [[Silent Knight (band)|Silent Knight]], [[Lord (band)|Lord]], [[Psycroptic]], [[Megadeth]], [[Entombed (band)]], [[Abbath]], [[whitechapel (band)]], [[krisiun]], [[Northlane]],and [[Origin (band)|Origin]].

